Zdravo, tata!

5
00:00:53,760 --> 00:00:54,920
Još se nisi obukao?

6
00:01:04,160 --> 00:01:05,560
Martane, čekaj!

7
00:01:06,960 --> 00:01:08,840
- Evo!
- Uobičajeno?

8
00:01:09,000 --> 00:01:11,040
Da, plus džem i puter.
Otišao sam.

9
00:01:11,200 --> 00:01:13,800
Da, obećavam
da ću otići u dućan posle časova.

10
00:01:21,880 --> 00:01:23,560
Hej ti! Idemo!

11
00:01:24,560 --> 00:01:25,840
Dobro si. Hajdemo!

12
00:01:26,360 --> 00:01:27,400
Vas troje,

13
00:01:27,460 --> 00:01:29,100
zar niste čuli zvono?

14
00:01:47,120 --> 00:01:49,280
- Koliko?
- 100 franaka.

15
00:02:33,160 --> 00:02:36,040
Bio je u nesvesti.
Ne može da kaže ni reč.

16
00:02:36,200 --> 00:02:37,320
Kad se to dogodilo?

17
00:02:37,480 --> 00:02:40,360
Pre par sati.
Profesor fizičkog ga je našao.

18
00:02:40,520 --> 00:02:43,160
Dali smo mu tabletu protiv bolova.

19
00:02:51,440 --> 00:02:52,760
Pao sam.

20
00:02:52,960 --> 00:02:54,280
Ne verujem ti.

21
00:02:57,840 --> 00:02:58,920
Čekaj, pomoći ću ti.

22
00:03:00,560 --> 00:03:01,680
Da li si dobro?

23
00:03:02,280 --> 00:03:03,320
Da.

24
00:03:04,000 --> 00:03:05,400
Tukao si se?

25
00:03:07,040 --> 00:03:08,160
Hajde onda.

26
00:03:10,160 --> 00:03:11,600
Vodim te kući.

27
00:03:14,440 --> 00:03:15,840
Da li daleko stanuješ?

28
00:03:16,000 --> 00:03:18,280
Ne, pet minuta odavde, ovuda.

29
00:03:26,440 --> 00:03:28,760
Čime se baviš osim što si pozornik?

30
00:03:28,920 --> 00:03:30,280
Ja ovo radim zbog para.

31
00:03:30,440 --> 00:03:32,760
Ali zaista želim da predajem istoriju,

32
00:03:32,960 --> 00:03:35,800
ako položim prijemni,
ići ću na fakultet.

33
00:03:36,240 --> 00:03:38,480
- A ako padneš?
- Neću.

34
00:03:41,000 --> 00:03:44,280
- U kom is razredu?
- Trećem.

35
00:03:44,440 --> 00:03:46,840
- Diploma je u rukama.
- Da.

36
00:03:53,200 --> 00:03:55,720
- Ovo je tvoj ranac.
- Pst, moj tata spava.

37
00:04:04,960 --> 00:04:06,320
Ti snimaš filmove?

38
00:04:06,680 --> 00:04:08,280
- Pomalo, da.
- Mogu li?

39
00:04:11,680 --> 00:04:13,360
Držiš ga kao dvogled?

40
00:04:17,840 --> 00:04:18,960
Da li ja sad snimam?

41
00:04:19,120 --> 00:04:21,040
Ne, prestani, ja ne volim to.

42
00:04:25,240 --> 00:04:27,040
Moram da se vratim u školu.

43
00:04:29,760 --> 00:04:31,360
Čuvaj se, odmori se.

44
00:04:32,080 --> 00:04:33,280
Vidimo se sutra.

45
00:04:53,440 --> 00:04:56,560
Nisi kupio ništa.
Reci mi zašto?

46
00:04:59,240 --> 00:05:00,320
Zaboravio sam.

47
00:05:00,480 --> 00:05:01,520
Zaboravio si?

48
00:05:01,800 --> 00:05:04,200
Kad ja ujutru dođem kući, 
umirem od gladi.

49
00:05:04,360 --> 00:05:06,880
- Mogu li da računam na tebe, ili ne?
- Da, tata.

50
00:05:08,240 --> 00:05:09,880
Gledaš TV celo veče?

51
00:05:10,040 --> 00:05:12,760
- Nemaš ništa za domaći?
- Ali, tata, molim te!

52
00:05:13,320 --> 00:05:14,640
"Tata, molim te!"

53
00:05:18,800 --> 00:05:19,960
Idiot.

54
00:05:46,760 --> 00:05:48,200
<i>Šta ti tamo radiš?</i>

55
00:05:58,360 --> 00:05:59,680
Oh, sranje.

56
00:06:08,880 --> 00:06:09,920
Ovo je dobro.

57
00:06:10,080 --> 00:06:11,680
- Dve sekunde!
- Izlazi napolje, odmah!

58
00:06:11,840 --> 00:06:14,160
Sačekaj minut, telefoniram.

59
00:06:14,320 --> 00:06:16,480
- Idi u razred.
- Ima još 15 minuta.

60
00:06:16,640 --> 00:06:18,680
Baš me briga što ima još 15 minuta.

61
00:06:18,840 --> 00:06:20,600
- Požuri.
- Skini mi se!

62
00:06:20,760 --> 00:06:22,280
Ne mogu da telefoniram na miru?

63
00:06:36,400 --> 00:06:37,680
- Hvala.
- Srećno.

64
00:06:41,280 --> 00:06:42,960
Siril Kolar: Divlje noći

65
00:06:43,020 --> 00:06:45,020
Štefan Cvajg: Pomešana osećanja
Jukio Mišima: Zabranjene boje

66
00:06:45,080 --> 00:06:46,100
Dobar dan.

67
00:06:48,640 --> 00:06:49,800
Da li ti je bolje?

68
00:06:50,040 --> 00:06:51,240
Dobro sam.

69
00:06:51,400 --> 00:06:52,680
Ne boli te?

70
00:06:53,280 --> 00:06:54,400
Malo.

71
00:06:56,680 --> 00:07:00,200
- Ovo nije školska lektira.
- Ne. To je za mene.

72
00:07:05,440 --> 00:07:06,520
Dobro. Zdravo, onda.

73
00:07:07,960 --> 00:07:09,080
Zdravo.

74
00:07:11,080 --> 00:07:12,000
Zdravo.

75
00:07:16,720 --> 00:07:18,560
- Prijatan dan.
- Hvala, zdravo.

76
00:08:01,520 --> 00:08:04,720
Slušaj, moj posao je bio 
da te odvedem kući.

77
00:08:05,560 --> 00:08:08,560
Ja sad nisam na poslu.
Moj radni dan je prošao. Razumeš?

78
00:08:12,720 --> 00:08:14,600
Koliko zarađuješ za ovo?

79
00:08:15,360 --> 00:08:17,160
3,500 franaka, nepuno radno vreme.

80
00:08:17,480 --> 00:08:18,520
Zašto?

81
00:08:20,880 --> 00:08:23,080
Imam 150 franaka 
koje možeš da zaradiš.

82
00:08:23,360 --> 00:08:24,400
Molim?

83
00:08:31,400 --> 00:08:34,880
Izlazi napolje! Izlazi, gubi se!
Izlazi napolje!

84
00:09:33,200 --> 00:09:35,520
Tvoja kuća je tamo 
desno, zar ne?

85
00:09:38,520 --> 00:09:40,360
Zašto si se predomislio?

86
00:10:01,960 --> 00:10:03,160
Šta ti hoćeš?

87
00:10:05,400 --> 00:10:06,480
Da glumim ženu?

88
00:10:07,640 --> 00:10:09,960
Ja ponekad to radim s mojom devojkom.

89
00:10:12,280 --> 00:10:13,400
Prestani, neću to.

90
00:10:14,120 --> 00:10:15,360
Popuši mi onda.

91
00:10:17,800 --> 00:10:18,840
Hajde.

92
00:10:41,920 --> 00:10:44,000
Izvini, nisam mislio da je to ovako.

93
00:10:48,080 --> 00:10:49,440
Kako si mislio da je to?

94
00:10:52,760 --> 00:10:53,920
Ne ovako.

95
00:11:53,520 --> 00:11:55,280
Siguran si da to želiš?

96
00:12:25,840 --> 00:12:27,520
Stavi kremu na ovo.

97
00:12:27,680 --> 00:12:30,400
Modrice neće proći same od sebe.

98
00:12:35,440 --> 00:12:36,680
Podigni noge.

99
00:12:39,680 --> 00:12:40,920
Opusti se.

100
00:12:43,960 --> 00:12:46,160
- Opusti se.
- Sačekaj sekund.

101
00:12:47,960 --> 00:12:49,520
Savi se malo u leđima.

102
00:12:50,840 --> 00:12:51,920
Savi se.

103
00:12:52,080 --> 00:12:53,680
- Ovako?
- Da.

104
00:12:57,240 --> 00:12:58,360
A sad polako.

105
00:13:00,280 --> 00:13:02,120
- Čekaj.
- Smiri se.

106
00:13:07,880 --> 00:13:08,960
Okreni se.

107
00:15:52,480 --> 00:15:53,600
Dođi ovamo, ti!

108
00:15:54,720 --> 00:15:56,960
- Da li si ti isključio muziku?
- Da.

109
00:15:57,120 --> 00:15:59,120
Isključio si muziku tvog domaćina?

110
00:15:59,280 --> 00:16:00,360
Da, ja sam takav.

111
00:16:00,520 --> 00:16:01,800
Sutra me nećeš poznavati.

112
00:16:01,960 --> 00:16:04,040
<i>Čemu sva ta mržnja?</i>
<i>To nije vredno.</i>

113
00:16:04,200 --> 00:16:05,960
<i>Šurik ti nije rekao</i>
<i>Muškarci su isti.</i>

114
00:16:06,120 --> 00:16:08,080
Čuješ me?
Prođi pored mene sutra.

115
00:16:11,880 --> 00:16:13,880
Zašto se ne ponašaš 
kao klinci tvojih godina?

116
00:16:14,040 --> 00:16:15,100
Kako se oni ponašaju?

117
00:16:15,160 --> 00:16:17,560
Oni ne provode dane snimajuću ljude.

118
00:16:17,880 --> 00:16:20,320
Ne prate momke po hodniku.

119
00:16:20,480 --> 00:16:23,200
- Idi u klubove, zabavljaj se.
- Ne mogu. Bole me uši.

120
00:16:23,360 --> 00:16:25,320
Ti ne ideš na zabave, ne pušiš.
Dosadan si.

121
00:16:25,480 --> 00:16:26,760
Tako je.

122
00:16:26,920 --> 00:16:28,440
Kad se tvoj tata vraća?

123
00:16:28,600 --> 00:16:29,960
7:30.

124
00:16:30,480 --> 00:16:32,080
Ostalo nam je još dva sata.

125
00:16:39,240 --> 00:16:40,240
Prestani!

126
00:17:07,760 --> 00:17:09,040
<i>Divan brod.</i>

127
00:17:09,200 --> 00:17:11,320
"Želim da ti kažem razmažena vilo,

128
00:17:11,480 --> 00:17:13,320
"Razne lepote krase tvoju mladost

129
00:17:13,600 --> 00:17:16,920
"Da naslikam tvoju lepotu,
detinjstvo pomešano s zrelošću."

130
00:17:17,080 --> 00:17:19,440
Hvala, Aurelien. Sad, Florine.

131
00:17:19,600 --> 00:17:21,720
"Kad uskovitlaš vazduh 
svojom širokom suknjom,

132
00:17:21,880 --> 00:17:24,920
"kao doteran brod koji isplovljava 
na more pod punim jedrima

133
00:17:25,080 --> 00:17:27,840
"i valja se lenjo
u sporom, lakom ritmu."

134
00:17:28,440 --> 00:17:29,500
Uđite.

135
00:17:30,200 --> 00:17:33,320
Izvinite, upravnik želi da vidi
Martana Bovara.

136
00:17:33,480 --> 00:17:34,560
Martin.

137
00:17:36,160 --> 00:17:37,440
Uzmi tvoje stvari.

138
00:17:45,520 --> 00:17:46,760
- Doviđenja.
- Doviđenja.

139
00:18:52,000 --> 00:18:55,120
- Zdravi, tata.
- Martane, dođi malo ovamo.

140
00:19:02,040 --> 00:19:03,480
Šta je ovo dođavola?

141
00:19:04,080 --> 00:19:05,320
Možeš li da objasniš?

142
00:19:08,360 --> 00:19:09,480
Da li se drogiraš?

143
00:19:12,280 --> 00:19:14,920
Martane, pitao sam te,
da li se drogiraš?

144
00:19:18,040 --> 00:19:19,280
Ne, to nije moje.

145
00:19:20,680 --> 00:19:22,400
Ti si ga izgubio. Vidi.

146
00:19:23,080 --> 00:19:25,280
Prazan frižider.
Molio sam te četiri puta.

147
00:19:25,440 --> 00:19:28,480
Šta se dešava u ovoj kući?
Šta je s tobom, Martane?

148
00:19:48,120 --> 00:19:49,140
Stoj.

149
00:19:56,600 --> 00:19:58,240
Gde su moje? Pozadi?

150
00:20:08,560 --> 00:20:10,240
- Hoćeš još?
- U redu onda!

151
00:20:52,360 --> 00:20:54,760
Dobro je kad provodimo vreme zajedno.

152
00:20:54,920 --> 00:20:56,520
Stalno smo se mimoilazili.

153
00:20:59,760 --> 00:21:00,820
Hvala.

154
00:21:03,600 --> 00:21:04,640
Izvoli.

155
00:21:09,880 --> 00:21:12,600
Sad vidiš kako je to.

156
00:21:13,160 --> 00:21:16,080
Možeš da dođeš da radiš 
sa mnom za vreme raspusta.

157
00:21:16,240 --> 00:21:17,880
Da zaradiš džeparac.

158
00:21:18,040 --> 00:21:21,400
I to je kul, ne brini,
ništa se veliko ne dešava noću.

159
00:21:31,720 --> 00:21:34,080
Znaš da sam i ja bio u tvojim godinama.

160
00:21:34,240 --> 00:21:36,200
Svi smo mi grešili na svoj način.

161
00:21:37,320 --> 00:21:40,800
Ali uz sve ovo na TV, pazi se.

162
00:21:43,040 --> 00:21:44,720
Obećaj mi da ćeš se čuvati.

163
00:21:46,840 --> 00:21:47,920
Martane?

164
00:21:53,240 --> 00:21:54,400
Obećavam.

165
00:22:31,600 --> 00:22:32,660
Oh, ne.

166
00:22:34,280 --> 00:22:36,240
Ponašaj se kao da te ne snimam.

167
00:22:36,520 --> 00:22:38,440
Ako ćeš da me snimaš, 
moraš da mi platiš.

168
00:22:38,600 --> 00:22:40,360
Upozoravam te, ozbiljan sam.

169
00:22:40,840 --> 00:22:43,400
Platiću ti ako ovo ikad 
iskoristim za nešto.

170
00:22:45,280 --> 00:22:46,880
Hajde, skloni to.

